{
  "texts": [
    "Table 5 presents performance results of various LLMs using different retrievers.",
    "GNN-RAG is the retrieval approach that achieves the overall best performance.",
    "For instance, GNN-RAG improves ChatGPT by up to 5.2% points at Hit over the best competing approach.",
    "Moreover, GNN-RAG substantially improves the KGQA performance of weaker LLMs, such as Alpaca-7B and Flan-T5-xl.",
    "The improvement over RoG is up to 13.2% points at Hit, while GNN-RAG outperforms Llama-70B approaches us- ing a lightweight Llama-7B model."
  ]
}